name: Sonics Skater 04
description: I love that you can still see fans wearing Seattle SuperSonics basketball jerseys out in the city. This piece is based on a guy I saw skating around Alki Beach. You can relocate a team but not the fandom. Long live the Reign Man!  2500 x 2500 gif, analog pen, digital color. Created in Seattle, WA. Copyright @mightymoss.
